queries.sql: SELECT `movies`.*, `movies`.*, SUM(visitors.views) as views FROM `movies` JOIN `visitors` ON `visitors`.`movie_id` = `movies`.`id` LEFT JOIN `links` as `l` ON `l`.`movie_id` = `movies`.`id` WHERE `movies`.`status` = 'public' AND `movies`.`type` = 'movie' AND movies.created_at >= DATE_SUB(DATE(NOW()), INTERVAL 45 DAY) AND `l`.`is_broken` = 0 AND `movies`.`status` = 'public' GROUP BY `movies`.`id` ORDER BY `visitors`.`views` DESC, `movies`.`updated_at` DESC LIMIT 6

SELECT DISTINCT `movies`.*, `seasons`.`season`, `seasons`.`series_id`, `series`.`title` as `series_title`, `series`.`imdb_id` as `series_imdb_id`, `series`.`tmdb_id` as `series_tmdb_id`, `seasons`.`series_id`, SUM(`visitors`.`views`) AS `views` FROM `movies` LEFT JOIN `seasons` ON `seasons`.`id` = `movies`.`season_id` LEFT JOIN `series` ON `series`.`id` = `seasons`.`series_id` JOIN `visitors` ON `visitors`.`movie_id` = `movies`.`id` LEFT JOIN `links` as `l` ON `l`.`movie_id` = `movies`.`id` WHERE `movies`.`type` = 'episode' AND `movies`.`status` = 'public' AND movies.created_at >= DATE_SUB(DATE(NOW()), INTERVAL 45 DAY) AND `l`.`is_broken` = 0 AND `movies`.`status` = 'public' GROUP BY `movies`.`id`, `seasons`.`series_id` ORDER BY `views` DESC, `movies`.`updated_at` DESC LIMIT 6
